Resource Profile: Audit Event for Update DocumentMetadata Transaction at Source

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epr-fhir/StructureDefinition/ch-mhd-updatedocumentmetadata-audit-source Version: 4.0.1-ballot
Active as of 2024-05-16 Computable Name: AuditUpdateDocumentMetadataSource

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

Defines constraints on the AuditEvent Resource to record when a updatedocumentmetadata Transaction happens at the Source.

  • Export event
  • shall have source of itself
  • shall have a document source agent
  • shall have a document recipient agent
  • may have user, app, organization agent(s)
  • shall have a patient entity
  • shall have a submission set identity entity

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
